title: A Picturesque residence w/in-unit W&D, open floorplan & walk to Trans!
posting_body: ['This quaint, garden residence in Pacific Heights boasts soaring ceilings and room to comfortably sleep, work and entertain - all in one place.', 'The generous floorplan, dual walk-in closets, in-unit laundry and ample storage gives this studio more flexible use of space than most one bedrooms.', 'The kitchen offers plenty of counter space and a pass-through breakfast bar makes for a nice flow into the great room.', 'The bathroom features a tiled shower over tub.', 'This home makes a great pied-a-tierre or city home and is well located moments to Polk and Union Street shops, restaurants, artisanal coffee, Lafayette Park, Whole Foods and so much more.', 'Half a block to MUNI, corporate shuttles, and all the North side has to offer!', 'A perfect retreat in the heart of it all!']
